==English==
===Noun===
'''candela'''

#In the [[International System of Units]], the [[base unit]] of [[luminous intensity]]; the luminous intensity, in a given direction, of a source that emits [[monochromatic]] [[radiation]] of [[frequency]] 540 &times; 10<sup>12</sup> [[hertz]] and that has a [[radiant]] [[intensity]] in that direction of 1/683 [[watt]] per [[steradian]].  Symbol: cd

